<section id="fs-id2578179" type="ap-test-prep" class="ap-test-prep">
<title>Test Prep for AP Courses</title>
<exercise id="fs-id1766256" type="ap-test-prep">
<problem id="fs-id1381252">
<para id="fs-id2584427">What is the difference between the waves coming from a tuning fork and electromagnetic waves?</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-id1307817">
<para id="fs-id1235277">The waves coming from a tuning fork are mechanical waves that are longitudinal in nature, whereas electromagnetic waves are transverse in nature.</para>
</solution>
</exercise>

